32:42.842 --> 32:44.082
Saya akan tengok hari ini.

32:44.683 --> 32:45.282
Bagus.

32:47.362 --> 32:48.762
Apa rancangan kamu?

32:51.203 --> 32:53.723
Bida tanah North Waichuan.

32:54.602 --> 32:56.683
