36:14.283 --> 36:15.122
Tak perlu takut.

36:18.562 --> 36:19.923
Bawa dokumen

36:19.923 --> 36:21.162
tentang pinjaman kredit bank.

36:21.722 --> 36:22.242
Ini.

36:22.522 --> 36:23.042
Ini.

36:24.202 --> 36:25.162
Endorsemen ini...

36:25.483 --> 36:25.883
Baik.

36:26.242 --> 36:27.323
