36:27.763 --> 36:29.162
Nombor sembilan.

36:29.264 --> 36:29.744
(Objektif dan Kepentingan Projek)

36:30.602 --> 36:31.242
Catatkan ini.

36:32.403 --> 36:33.323
Berita baik!

36:34.202 --> 36:34.763
Encik Chen

36:34.843 --> 36:36.082
