36:36.722 --> 36:37.162
Betul ke?

36:37.763 --> 36:38.323
Hebat!

36:44.003 --> 36:44.602
Macam mana?

36:45.042 --> 36:45.763
Boleh ikut rentak?

36:46.843 --> 36:47.483
Encik Huang.

36:48.042 --> 36:49.483
Setiap tahun kamu lari maraton,

36:50.042 --> 36:50.963
